<p>
<note n="0723003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723003">品＋（之十四）【明】</note>
<note n="0723004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723004">不分卷【和】</note>
<note n="0723005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723005">Vimalaprabha.</note>
<note n="0723006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723006">彼劫＝劫被【和】</note>
<note n="0723007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723007">Pralambabāhu.</note>
<note n="0723008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0723008">Vidyuddatta.</note>
